summary 'Mailclient Module'
description 'The **MailClient** module configures a postfix mail relay *for local
clients only*. It will also forward email addressed to root on the
puppet client to another address which is configurable in Hiera.'
project_page 'https://stash.adaptavist.com/projects/PUP/repos/puppet-mailclient'

